[[File:Impling jar detail.png|left|90px]]
An '''impling jar''' is a [[butterfly jar]] treated with [[Imp repellent|Imp Repellent]]. These jars are used to catch [[implings]] in both the [[Impetuous Impulses]] [[minigame]] and all over [[Gielinor]]. When opening a caught impling in a jar, the jar has a 10% chance of being destroyed.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1059259735675932672|date=4 November 2018|archiveurl=https://archive.vn/rpWRS|archivedate=23 July 2019|quote=[What are the chances of an impling jar breaking when opening it?] 10% flat rate, I think.}}

Impling jars '''cannot''' be used to catch [[Butterfly (Hunter)|butterflies]].

